NAME
    App::Dochazka::Common - Dochazka Attendance and Time Tracking System
    shared modules

VERSION
    Version 0.191

DESCRIPTION
    This distro contains modules that are used by both the server
    App::Dochazka::REST and the command-line client App::Dochazka::CLI.

PACKAGE VARIABLES AND EXPORTS
FUNCTIONS
  init_timepiece
    (Re-)initialize the date/time-related package variables

